text: Jesper Stålheim (born 23 March 1988) is a Swedish competitive sailor. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, in the men's Laser class where he finished in 16th place. He has qualified to represent Sweden at the 2020 Summer Olympics in the men's Laser class. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish male sailors (sport) Category:Olympic sailors of Sweden Category:Sailors at the 2016 Summer Olympics – Laser
